{"tid":2096467,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文字直播］電單車手足被押上法庭 有黑警手持衝鋒槍威嚇在場記者","createTime":"2020-07-06T06:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T07:56:15.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ab12988093ec45e088156bafae4b39969b78874a","tid":2096467,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T06:52:38.000Z","msg":"【國安法首疑犯上庭 警持衝鋒槍拉扯記者】<br />\n<br />\n今日國安法首名疑犯提堂，西九龍裁判法院外大批記者守候。約14時20分，三架警車護送下，由一架私家車押送到法庭。<br />\n<br />\n大批記者上前包圍拍攝，其他警車內的警員落車，拉扯記者。有頭戴防彈頭盔的警員，更加手持衝鋒槍威嚇，亦有警員對記者指罵。有記者要求警方冷靜，警方則大聲回應「係你哋唔冷靜啊！」，場面一度混亂。<br />\n<br />\n攝/ Tsukushi Wu<br />\n<br />\n#DBC #DBChannel #加山傳播 #國安法 #香港警察 #新聞自由 #賞花行人路<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109301110486297/posts/275965093819897/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109301110486297%2Fposts%2F275965093819897%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FipZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=05e603b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109301110486297/posts/275965093819897/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"228bf8df1f776122f17686f42856626ecb8d4129","tid":2096467,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6002b3821594ebcc60c0b07a8b10ad8daa2049","tid":2096467,"uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"#西九龍裁判法院第三庭 <br />\n<br />\n1500開庭<br />\n<br />\n4警押手足上庭🌚"},{"pid":"5bd2022ca7b3dab836f6241a6e5d480594ef994f","tid":2096467,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:13:44.000Z","msg":"7.1 當日駕駛插入「光復香港 時代革命」旗的電單車，被指撞向警員，被控「煽動他人分裂國家罪」及「恐怖活動罪」的 23